data.description: Welcome to 16508 Charles Town Dr, where the most beautiful sunsets await you.  This charming two-story colonial offers over 1800 sqft, that includes 5 bedrooms and 2.5 baths.  Step inside to a spacious living area filled with natural light. The open concept layout connects the living room to the dining area, perfect for entertaining. The stylish kitchen features ample cabinet space and modern appliances.  Upstairs you'll find 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths, including the spacious master with a private bath and walk-in closet.  Escape downstairs to a recently finished basement that includes a 5th bedroom, play room and storage space.  Outside, the backyard is a calm oasis with a private backyard, fire pit, and patio where you'll fall in love with the most stunning sunsets.   This peaceful neighborhood is located within minutes from several lakes, restaurants, shopping and expressways.   Don't miss this opportunity to make 16508 Charles Town Dr. your new home.
